> **Strategic Takeaway:** The [workflow](/process) is automatic. The ticket routes itself. The escalation happens itself. The follow-up reminds itself. The agent does not think about the process. The teams that build visible infrastructure are the ones whose agents fight the system. The teams that build invisible infrastructure are the ones whose agents serve the customer. Surface the knowledge. Connect the tools. Automate the workflow. The infrastructure becomes invisible. The agents become effective.

